<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Excellently" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Excellently,</orth> 1) eminently, extremely well: <bibl n="shak. ado 3.4.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 4, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.237" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 237</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 185</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 185</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.206" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 206</bibl>.<lb />2) in a high degree: <cit><quote>no man alive can love in such a sort the thing he means to kill more e.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.1.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 1, 24</bibl></cit> (cf. <emph>Excellence,</emph> def. 2).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>